INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('1', 'What is Synergy?', 'Synergy is a central, open, transparent, efficient and convenient international logistics data exchange platform and a supply chain financial service platform, which is established by the block chain, the Internet of things and large data technology. It aims to provide comprehensive services such as logistics tracking, information inquiry, cross-border payment and supply chain financing for international logistics and international trade related individuals, enterprises and government agencies.', '1532592132');
INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('2', 'What are the core advantages of Synergy?', 'The core advantage of Synergy lies in the following aspects:\n1, scientific framework: basic public chain + Intelligent contract scientific structure, and solve logistics, information flow + capital flow.\n2, a reasonable mechanism: a reasonable \"dislocation incentive\" mechanism, to guide individuals, enterprises and government agencies to participate in the construction of flat ends.\n3, rich resources: over twenty years of cross-border supply chain experience, the support of a number of international freight forwarders alliance, the resources of more than 7 million foreign trade customers in dozens of countries and regions\n4. Professional team: professional team. The strong combination of the block chain technology team and the international supply chain team.', '1532657960');
INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('3', 'What are the values of the Synergy token?', 'It provides a good token incentive mechanism for some enterprise data link, and enables the supply chain to develop healthily and rapidly. The use of token as a credit card financing system can solve the problem of capital flow for some small and medium-sized enterprises. We can use tokens to participate in cross-border settlement.', '1532657967');
INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('4', 'What is the construction process of Synergy international logistics data query platform? What size of the journey will be in the future?', 'Supported by powerful entity international trading company, it has been rapidly integrated into the Synergy international logistics query platform through existing data. At the same time, we use token to encourage other freight forwarding companies to upload data, and further improve the integrated logistics chain data query platform.\nIn the future, all the logistics information will be integrated into the Synergy platform, and the information of each link will be querying with the block chain.', '1532657986');
INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('7', 'Why does the Synergy project choose the supply chain industry as the breakthrough point?', 'The supply chain is a huge, tedious, long and market prospect system. The use of Synergy\'s original token can make all links more convenient to connect. The block chain network can solve industry pain fairly and transparently. It can better serve supply chain finance and integrate the supply chain quickly on a complete and efficient chain system, which is more convenient for economic circulation.', '1532662890');
INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('8', 'When Synergy is applied more and more widely, how can Synergy deal with potential huge trading load? How can Synergy expand?', 'The ability of the main chain to deal with the transaction load, compared with the ether workshop, is currently using the PoW total mechanism. The average block time is about 30S, the average transaction number is from dozens to hundreds, and the number of transactions in one day is close to 500 thousand, which has met most of the demand in the public chain application scene; and the Synergy owner is the main requirement. The chain adopts the PoST+PoW consensus mechanism, the load can be greater, the load can be loaded on a larger scale, on the other hand, Synergy is designed with double layer structure, and the transaction data and logistics data are stratified management. Synergy itself is designed to target an extensible and large scale ecosystem, so the expansion of Synergy\'s scale is very expansible.', '1532663507');
INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('9', 'How does Synergy plan to solve the property rights problems in the supply chain finance field, and how to ensure the safety of funds?', 'The most important thing in the supply chain is the bill of lading. When the enterprise applies for financing, it needs the pledge of the bill of lading, and the real right of the goods belongs to the Synergy platform. The bill of lading is released after the end of the whole transaction. Through the destination of real right, the security of funds is guaranteed.', '1532663622');
INSERT INTO `e_faq` VALUES ('10', 'With the increasing recognition of Synergy globally, what strategy has Synergy adopted to enhance communication with its supporters? ', ' First, do a good job in Synergy brand management, and professionally answer all kinds of problems that need feedback in the development process of Synergy, and regularly exchange reports. Secondly, the Synergy team actively participates in various organizational activities and regularly meets with the media.', '1532663687');

